Feline2::

she watched as the beam of energy hit HotRod. She wsn't sure what 
they were doing to him. "LEAVE HIM ALONE!" She fired her optic lazars 
at Arcangle. "DON'T HURT HIM! PLEASE DON'T HURT HIM!" She clawed 
angrily at the net. "HOTROD!" She finally started to tear through the 
net, and climbed out of it. She ran over to HotRod. "Are you ok?"
